{"compat":{"partially-supported":[],"unsupported":[]},"constituent-properties":[{"target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top","text":"padding-top"},{"target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-right","text":"padding-right"},{"target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-bottom","text":"padding-bottom"},{"target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-left","text":"padding-left"}],"interactive-example":"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/css/padding.html","name":"padding","see-also":[{"target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_box_model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model","text":"Introduction to the CSS basic box model"},{"target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-top","text":"padding-top"},{"target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/padding-block-start","text":"padding-block-start"}],"status":[],"summary":"The <strong><code>padding</code></strong> <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Shorthand_properties\">shorthand property</a> sets the <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_box_model/Introduction_to_the_CSS_box_model#padding_area\">padding area</a> on all four sides of an element at once.","syntax-example":"/* Apply to all four sides */\npadding: 1em;\n\n/* top and bottom | left and right */\npadding: 5% 10%;\n\n/* top | left and right | bottom */\npadding: 1em 2em 2em;\n\n/* top | right | bottom | left */\npadding: 5px 1em 0 2em;\n\n/* Global values */\npadding: inherit;\npadding: initial;\npadding: revert;\npadding: revert-layer;\npadding: unset;\n"}